Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.43,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.60,0:00:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.06,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.48,0:02:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第62话 高深莫测的阿椿咒术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么抵抗都是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的\N成为妖怪的饵食吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不用铁碎牙就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种杂碎妖怪  单手就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴硬的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.69,0:03:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的性命还在我的手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题…没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  去帮助犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样戈薇会撑不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…椿不论犬夜叉赢或输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都打算咒杀戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.49,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  非得切断椿的咒术不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒椿  或打倒咒术媒介的式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇在倒下去之前曾说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被不知名的东西咬了一口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那可能就是黑巫女的式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是那条蛇没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  麻烦你掩护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔符吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做无谓的挣扎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢!我的咒术是不会破解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清楚情况的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗只会延长戈薇的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说到不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就送戈薇上路算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  振作点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…谁在叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  快点起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想睡到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会在这边的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡迷糊了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点起床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要吃早餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连早安都不会说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什么时候回到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有去过什么地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那边的世界啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百年前过去的世界啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是进入隐密的井里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到有很多妖怪的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你进去过那口井里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已经来回好几次了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连犬夜叉都有来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.01,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们连犬夜叉都忘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里长着狗耳朵的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  今天向学校请假比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡迷糊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  快迟到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的事情  全部都是梦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点精神都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在烦恼什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟男朋友处的不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了!你们还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生的事情对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  果然不是在作梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B班的北条同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.72,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爱吃醋又粗鲁任性的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇你脚踏两条船吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇真有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还搞不懂状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是突然回到原来的生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着念下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试快到了  别再发呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.63,0:08:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…我必须要准备考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我原本的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听说\N日暮同学没什么精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个对身体很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.79,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩踩看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是哪里不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这样下去不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要很多小孩呢\N讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶  买四魂之玉给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起这个四魂之玉的由来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从战国时代…\N走吧  奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蚋  我觉得自己怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.72,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许许多多的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脑海里转来转去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.09,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像有一件非做不可的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回忆起来的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈来愈模糊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.62,0:11:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直有一种不可以再这样下去的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.59,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到底是什么事非做不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时感受到的脖子的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也渐渐的习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思绪也变的无法止息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么觉得不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉  北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总算来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了这个而来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  那个标靶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的瞄准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架式不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的集中力不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…请问你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又会丧命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.61,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬…犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还无法离开这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.77,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这个的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界是你的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.45,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的集中力不够吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经能耐住咒缚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣传你是桔梗转世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不全是唬人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是真正的桔梗  刚才那一箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能确实的命中我才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底你不过是桔梗的赝品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是其他人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.74,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙  这么急着找死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去  戈薇会支持不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  能再稍微撑一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那两人大卸八块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会让你被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闪开  杂碎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  椿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧  椿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就能切断咒术吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.48,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的效力还存在着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杀了式神吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你们几个也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有妖怪在她的体内吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  留在戈薇的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神…该不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕!这些妖怪全都是诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.06,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.83,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神!咬断那女人的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.83,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会输给你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将式神打回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是咒术反噬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和桔梗一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会被这小丫头给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉被净化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片取出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.19,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片就那样给她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  马上就能取回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给黑巫女一个雪耻的机会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还蛮体贴的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗尽力量了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.16,0:21:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饲养的妖怪统统死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只差一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.90,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要有这颗四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让我的力量更加强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会打倒他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧  犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇十分疲倦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她一直和咒术抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起老是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.30,0:22:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要流多少泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.04,0:22:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.81,0:22:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.72,0:22:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.09,0:22:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.56,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.87,0:23:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.84,0:23:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.38,0:23:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.12,0:23:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.64,0:23:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.39,0:23:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.89,0:23:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑巫女椿还持有四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.39,0:23:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只有追过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.40,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿的同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红巫女与白巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有够天真的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.40,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.40,0:24:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我骗了戈薇与弥勒他们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.38,0:24:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在前的红白巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.65,0:24:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得好好振作了


